OL,3,CWoman feared test error would rob
OL,4,Cchildren of their mum
OL,6,FShe is currently on the waiting list
OL,7,Ffor a hysterectomy at just 40 years
OL,8,Fold.
OL,10,FShe said: "To be told that in fact it
OL,11,Fcould have been prevented. Every
OL,12,Fperson puts their trust in the system
OL,13,Fand then they have failed.
OL,15,F"It's scary. I feel very angry. This
OL,16,Fis my life. I'm having to consider
OL,17,Fhaving a hysterectomy. Something that
OL,18,FI never wanted to do.
OL,20,F"My children have watched me cry. They
OL,21,Fhave seen how my anxiety has been.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
