OL,6,F"You know coming up to appointments,
OL,7,Fnot sleeping at night, just constantly
OL,8,Fworrying.
OL,10,F"My yearly checkup was nearly two
OL,11,Fmonths ago and I'm still waiting on a
OL,12,Fletter for my appointment.
OL,14,FI could be sitting here with cancer
OL,15,Fagain and I don't know, because I
OL,16,Fcan't get an appointment to get it
OL,17,Fdone".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
