OL,3,CWoman feared test error would rob
OL,4,Cchildren of their mum
OL,6,FThe Southern Trust was forced to
OL,7,Fapologise and order a recall of tests
OL,8,Ffor 17,500 women for a period between
OL,9,F2008 and 2021.
OL,11,FIt was one of the biggest health
OL,12,Fscandals in UK history.
OL,14,F"This has caused women to have cancer
OL,15,Fit has cost women their lives. There
OL,16,Fare children that have been left out
OL,17,Fthere without their mothers.
OL,19,F"It's time to speak out. We need
OL,20,Fanswers. This has gone on too long,"
OL,21,FCaroline added.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
