OL,6,F"The impact it has is physically huge
OL,7,Fbut that's dealt with. That's over and
OL,8,Fdone with. It's the mental impact that
OL,9,Fcontinues", she said.
OL,11,FThe woman, aged in her forties,
OL,12,Fbelieves a public inquiry is the only
OL,13,Fway to find out what happened and
OL,14,Fensure it doesn't happen again.
OL,16,F"To know that it's preventable. It's
OL,17,Fjust everything. I've gone through the
OL,18,Fsurgeries, the stress, everything my
OL,19,Ffamily has been put through.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
