OL,6,FShe continued: "I think after
OL,7,Feverything I've been through I deserve
OL,8,Fto know why that's happened, who's
OL,9,Fresponsible for this and to make sure
OL,10,Fit's not going to happen again.
OL,12,F"I think the only way to do that is to
OL,13,Fhave a public inquiry, to get to the
OL,14,Fbottom of it, to make sure they don't
OL,15,Fmake the same mistakes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
